      "startTime": 106.86666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_01-smr014.m4a",
      "text": "ジュースかおしるこか、迷ってたんですけど\n甘いのが食べたくなったから、こっちにしました",
      "startTime": 109.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 112.66666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_01-smr015.m4a",
      "text": "一度食べたら病みつきですよ！\n{user}さんも試してみますか？",
      "startTime": 114.86666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね\n機会があれば食べてみます……はは",
      "startTime": 118.86666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 125.66666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_01-smr016.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ、さっそくいただきます！\nんっ……もぐ。温かくて美味しい～",
      "startTime": 125.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_canned-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1966.6666666666542,
          "startTime": 125.36666666666666
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 131.03333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "どうしたんですか{user}さん？",
      "startTime": 131.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_01-smr017.m4a",
      "text": "ひょっとして、食べたくなっちゃいました？",
      "startTime": 134.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "いえ……昔好きだったドラマで、奥山さんみたいに\n食べっぷりのいい子役がいたのを思い出しました",
      "startTime": 141.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 145.06666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_01-smr018.m4a",
      "text": "……え？",
      "startTime": 145.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 146.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
